"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-14-im-love-diving-a-olympic-winner-whatever-happens-21224651\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The prospect of theParisOlympics is an exciting one but not one which holds any fear for me now I have a new mentality and mindset.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prospect\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 12}, {\"ngram\": \"theParisOlympics\", \"from\": 16, \"to\": 32}, {\"ngram\": \"an exciting one\", \"from\": 36, \"to\": 51}, {\"ngram\": \"any fear\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"a new mentality\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 118}, {\"ngram\": \"mindset\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For so long, the Games felt a long way away, an overwhelming prospect with so many hurdles to clear beforehand.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 155}, {\"ngram\": \"an overwhelming prospect\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"so many hurdles\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not seem like a reality for so long.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a reality\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But now we are almost there.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a huge wave of stress off my shoulders after the national championships in December and although I spoke to my coach, I have also learnt to deal with the pressure by myself.\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge wave\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"my shoulders\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"the national championships\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also did not want to spoil my experience or lessen the importance of other competitions by thinking about theOlympicstoo soon and that approach helped me centre myself.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my experience\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"other competitions\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"that approach\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was always the end goal but a jam-packed schedule of nationals, followed by world championships and three World Cup legs stood in the way, plus a lot of travel, which can be the hardest part of being a professional athlete, but one I have learnt to live with and thrive on.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end goal\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 699}, {\"ngram\": \"a jam-packed schedule\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"nationals\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"world championships\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"three World Cup legs\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardest part\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional athlete\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You get to visit some amazing countries, experience such cool cultures and eat great food, so we can not complain!\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some amazing countries\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"such cool cultures\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"great food\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, now I am back in training with Paris as the end goal.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1106, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998179839787, \"rank\": 1.8201595996450627e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"the end goal\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am back on the ten-metre board, with a lot of support behind me.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ten-metre board\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The National Lottery supports us in so many different ways; one of which is providing us with the best support staff, including my strength and conditioning coach who helps me focus on strength-building and power training.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The National Lottery\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"so many different ways\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"the best support staff\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"my strength and conditioning coach\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"strength-building and power training\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is vital for me going into the Games.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I speak to my team-mates about the prospect of the Olympics, of course, but your own experience is so valuable because it's come from you.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my team-mates\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"the prospect\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"your own experience\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This cycle has been three years instead of four due to the 2020 Olympics taking place a year late because of the pandemic.\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This cycle\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Olympics\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"the pandemic\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know in all honestly if that has been a benefit or not.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a benefit\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another year would have brought a lot of stress, I suppose, and my progress has been good since my Olympic debut in Tokyo and I want to get this over and done with now.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998638846759241, \"rank\": 0.0001358368257637568, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another year\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"my progress\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"my Olympic debut\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no expectations on myself.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no expectations\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to enjoy it.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aged 16 and with internal battles being fought over my mental health, I did not enjoy myself in Tokyo in the slightest.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998638846759241, \"rank\": 0.0001358368257637568, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"internal battles\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"my mental health\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt my Olympic experience was robbed from me because of the lack of joy I felt.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my Olympic experience\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time I have no school work to distract me or focus on in parallel and no excuses, and that helps me.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no school work\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"parallel\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am in love with diving once again and I think any sportsperson would agree that when you love what you are doing, you train and therefore perform better.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"any sportsperson\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going into this Games completely changed.\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this Games\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in such a dark place last time and thank god for helping me through.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a dark place\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"god\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is another competition after all.\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another competition\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I look back and can see drastic change on my face - I was sad, depressed and anxious at the last Olympics.\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drastic change\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2681}, {\"ngram\": \"my face\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"the last Olympics\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a completely different person now, for the better.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a completely different person\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whatever happens in Paris, happens.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2827, \"end\": 2832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998179839787, \"rank\": 1.8201595996450627e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Whatever\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will not make or break me.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I 